data.description: This 4 bedroom, 2 bath, on a 2 acre tract in town provides a spacious yard and a 25x28 shop wired with electric. Located just a few blocks from the local grocery store, post office and medical center, this is a perfect family home! 1768 square feet, split floor plan, spacious dining area and bedrooms. A backyard, surrounded by trees, large enough for games, gardening and/or whatever fits your family! Take a look.
